          </div>
          <div purpose="flow-step">
            <div purpose="step-number">3</div>
            <p purpose="step-title">Roll out in rings</p>
            <p>Stage updates across deployment rings. Scope by role, subsidiary, or geography. Fast where you can, careful where you must.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="flow-step">
            <div purpose="step-number">4</div>
            <p purpose="step-title">Report</p>
            <p>Dashboards show what's out of date and how long it was exposed. Pipe to your data lake for deeper history.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

